{"tid":966573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡Irvins鹹蛋魚皮  附送炸壁虎","createTime":"2019-01-03T02:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T02:31:14.000Z","uid":122167,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f7473ad8a5c4e5fbb1f9ef138e4dd3596d910a25","tid":966573,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T02:00:20.000Z","msg":"知名新加坡零食商「Irvins Salted Egg」，出品了許多紅遍全球的零食，在這之中酥炸鹹蛋鮭魚皮更受到廣大喜愛，不過有泰國網友日前在其中吃到一隻酥炸壁虎，讓廠商急忙在官網上道歉，並表示會退費賠償。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，泰國曼谷一名女子霍洛薇（Jane Holloway），上（12）月29日時在網路上表示，其家人在吃鹹蛋鮭魚皮時，發現一個古怪的東西，起先他們以為是一隻小鮭魚的魚頭，不過接下來卻發現其身上有四肢，大驚原來這是一隻壁虎。<br />\n<br />\n因為這一包魚皮要價超過600台幣的關係，在曼谷當地享有「貴族級零食」的名號，這起事件很快被擴散，且整隻壁虎被完整炸過，也引起了「同一批產品都有問題」的說法，相關事件也讓廠商「Irvins Salted Egg」關注，除了緊急在官網上道歉外，也承諾會全額退費並進行賠償。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4bqfywue\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4bqfywue&h=1a065080&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b798f96e902c63b09585453f5f0a97c9072dd7e","tid":966573,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T02:01:29.000Z","msg":"好想食壁虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e828ca4a2bbce66cbd1cd187fab6ca7f8a7397d","tid":966573,"uid":49392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"千與千尋版"},{"pid":"9238996af53bf5410a037a09994423888eaea7e8","tid":966573,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844b89195d6167d1a47c876f5f97d7c8f34c622f","tid":966573,"uid":19712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-